<div class="verdict">
  <p>Bottom line — ship it after fixing the 4 blockers</p>
  <span>The plan's scope, technology choices, and file structure are correct. The 4 critical problems (no persistence, wrong terminal attach behavior, missing pre-flight validation, env not actually injected) must be resolved before implementation begins — they are not polish, they are load-bearing. Fix those, add the 5 missing pieces, and this plan becomes implementation-ready. Estimated additions: 3 new Rust files (~250 lines total) and 2 additions to the TypeScript store.</span>
